2. Response
***********
render_for_pipeline(partial, "", "") { |rendered_view| 
	<<-eos
		$(".foo").html(rendered_view);
	eos
}

Sidenote
* When writing javascript code in async partials, wrap it with Pipeline.queue(function(){ your code goes here })